      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model form uncertainty assessment not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "RANS k-omega SST turbulence model selected based on literature consensus for rotating machinery hemolysis applications. Formal model form uncertainty quantification deferred; not required at MRL 2."
